{"tid":2205832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國化工、長江三峽曾遭美國防部點名  美資行助中共軍企發債","createTime":"2020-09-17T05:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T05:48:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c38c9e3f74bca8534cae824d9d4fffdeb3940df","tid":2205832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200917/TZPNLZ46INAJDLZ57SS63YVW5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200917%2FTZPNLZ46INAJDLZ57SS63YVW5Q%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=9572d469\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200917%2FTZPNLZ46INAJDLZ57SS63YVW5Q%2F&h=0c26bfe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200917/TZPNLZ46INAJDLZ57SS63YVW5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中國化工、長江三峽曾遭美國防部點名 <br />\n美資行助中共軍企發債<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J7avm_eUeEZeodmzJVYFUUDaWFQ=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AGHGRIKJMJEILN46XD2EZIT3KM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ7avm_eUeEZeodmzJVYFUUDaWFQ%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAGHGRIKJMJEILN46XD2EZIT3KM.jpg&h=a01e9e61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美角力博弈僵局難解，被美國國防部列為「中共軍事公司」的中國化工與中國長江三峽集團，前日遭《華爾街日報》揭發一直透過外資大行發債融資，涉近41億美元。雖然美國國防部的企業清單不會牽涉任何制裁行動，但不排除引起政府注意，經草擬及通過法案後，特朗普便可實行制裁，查封「中共軍事公司」資產與截斷美元資金融資。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jQbz43Zm6RF8ilehQ8YWrzfvXbI=/1280x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QLQOW5T3FREBBPTOSHZ65L27EA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjQbz43Zm6RF8ilehQ8YWrzfvXbI%3D%2F1280x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQLQOW5T3FREBBPTOSHZ65L27EA.jpg&h=2220053f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中國化工於周一發行合共近30億美元的債券供投資者認購。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n該報道周二引述投行銷售文件指，中國化工集團於本周一發債「吸水」，分別發行值約24億美元（約186億港元）美元債，還有相當。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國銀行和高盛參與了中國化工集團的發債交易，多間歐洲和中資機構亦有份。至於中。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/apj4Jv08-bfqsInR-gvS8ViYWHA=/1329x813/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HH4PKP65PVDDLMMNDKJKOLXV2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fapj4Jv08-bfqsInR-gvS8ViYWHA%3D%2F1329x813%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHH4PKP65PVDDLMMNDKJKOLXV2A.jpg&h=e4a6a8ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多間外資行包括高盛在內，均有份參與中國化工集團的發債交易。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩軍企：美無阻礙融資<br />\n<br />\n據悉，中國化工集團及中國長江三峽集團發債文件指出，美國國防部暫沒有阻礙清單上的企業進行國際融資，而且集團沒有受到任何出口管制與經濟制裁，會如以往一樣支付和獲取資金。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部前日指，美國國防部名單沒有任何證據或法律依據，濫用國家力量打。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n曾任美國貿易代表辦公室的助理法律顧問、現職霍金路偉的國際貿易事務律師Benjamin Kostrzewa表示，美國國防部的「中共軍。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RNGMtbo0xMkFu9DZVcTQnANflVk=/643x514/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EGWZOUOJUVB6XARMG2B37K5YYQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRNGMtbo0xMkFu9DZVcTQnANflVk%3D%2F643x514%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEGWZOUOJUVB6XARMG2B37K5YYQ.gif&h=63299238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特朗普隨時實施制裁<br />\n<br />\n而外資大行跟華府針對目標仍有生意來往，還有認購美國國防部清單上的中國企。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中美針鋒相對，但華爾街大行利字當頭，積極進軍中國市場，尤其中國加快開放金融市場，讓外資更容易買賣A股，為大行開拓新收費財源。彭博數據顯示，去年美國五大銀行於中國業務敞口共708億美元。"},{"pid":"515a9cda8019b26296de62c541612e676aad4a2c","tid":2205832,"uid":24356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:48:41.000Z","msg":"快啲啦喂"}]}